            "title": "Anthropic nears $1.5B joint venture with Blackstone, Goldman Sachs for AI tools",
            "body": "Anthropic, Blackstone and Hellman & Friedman are anchoring the deal (~$300M each). Goldman Sachs is investing ~$150M. The JV will develop and sell AI tools to private equity-backed companies using a Palantir-style consulting model.",
            "sources": [
              "https://www.reuters.com/legal/transactional/anthropic-nears-15-billion-ai-joint-venture-with-wall-street-firms-wsj-reports-2026-05-04/",
