            ]
          },
          {
            "title": "Pentagon inks AI deals with 7 tech companies \u2014 Anthropic excluded",
            "body": "The Pentagon reached agreements with Amazon Web Services, Google, Microsoft, OpenAI, SpaceX, NVIDIA, Reflection, and Oracle to deploy their AI on classified military networks. Anthropic was notably absent due to its legal dispute with the Pentagon over safety guardrails and mass surveillance concerns.",
            "sources": [
