              "https://thehackernews.com/2026/04/anthropic-mcp-design-vulnerability.html"
            ]
          },
          {
            "title": "AI outperforms doctors in Harvard emergency triage trial",
            "body": "Researchers tested an AI model against physicians in diagnosing hospital patients, and the model outperformed the humans. The study suggests a future 'triadic care model' of doctor, patient, and AI working together.",
