          {
            "title": "Big Tech AI spending set to hit $600B \u2014 investors question payoff",
            "body": "Reuters reports Big Tech has spent hundreds of billions over three years powering the AI boom. Meta alone could spend $145B this year on AI. Goldman Sachs says the AI software sell-off was overdone, calling it a buying opportunity.",
